generateName() - Static method in class aoop.asteroids.Utils
Function that generates a nice-looking (First or Last) name.
Readability is improved by alternating between a vowel and a consonant.
Vowels that are common in the English language have a higher chance to end up in the names.
Names have between 3 and 12 characters.
This function always terminates.

getMirrorLocations(double, double) - Method in class aoop.asteroids.model.gameobjects.GameObject
This function returns a Collection of possibly multiple locations at which a graphical representation of this GameObject should be drawn.
By drawing each of these, we ensure that objects that are half across the screen edge will draw their other half at the other side of the screen.
